descriptionHtml:
Friends have been bugging me for the ENB preset I use on my streams.
This is my own preset, after 2 weeks of tweaking I've decided to share it.

[youtube]-9GctUJ6HAU[/youtube]

Added some extra info by request of Kuldebar
-- Latest ENB as of .254
-- I'm using Enhanced Lights and FX in the screenshots
-- Small performance drop for me of 1-3FPS in most areas. I'm on an i7 950 @ 3.07 GHz, 16GB ram, and a single NVIDIA GeForce GTX 660 Ti
-- This ENB preset is meant to make Skyrim feel colder, the vanilla lighting gives everything a warm orange feel and I wanted more contrast between colours.
-- Nights I think are a bit brighter dungeons/interiors are darker than vanilla and look quite dramatic.
author: TechieJunk
